OL,3,CMilitary gap years for school-leavers
OL,4,Cto be introduced before general
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FMilitary gap years will be introduced
OL,8,Ffor school and college leavers before
OL,9,Fthe next general election, the defence
OL,10,Fsecretary has confirmed to ITV News.
OL,12,FThe UK has been investing heavily in
OL,13,Fdefence since Russia invaded Ukraine,
OL,14,Fin a bid to be prepared should a wider
OL,15,Fwar break out in Europe - but all
OL,16,Fthree branches of the UK armed forces
OL,17,Fare currently below their target size,
OL,18,Fand recruitment has proved a struggle.
