OL,7,FThe Strategic Defence Review (SDR),
OL,8,Fcommissioned by Prime Minister Keir
OL,9,FStarmer upon taking office,
OL,10,Frecommended several policies aimed at
OL,11,Fmaking the UK "warfighting ready"
OL,12,Fbecause the "threat we now face is
OL,13,Fmore serious and less predictable than
OL,14,Fat any time since the Cold War".
OL,16,FPart of that plan is to "end the
OL,17,Fhollowing out of the UK's Armed
OL,18,FForces" by hitting staffing targets,
OL,19,Fwhich would involve hiring at least
OL,20,F8,590 personnel.
