OL,3,CMilitary gap years for school-leavers
OL,4,Cto be introduced before general
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe SDR said Ministry of Defence
OL,8,Fofficials should look at the voluntary
OL,9,Fmilitary gap year model used in
OL,10,FAustralia, when considering how to
OL,11,Ffind more recruits.
OL,13,FNow Defence Secretary John Healey has
OL,14,Fconfirmed to ITV News that he's
OL,15,Faccepted the recommendation and wants
OL,16,Fthe scheme introduced before the next
OL,17,Fgeneral election, which is expected by
OL,18,F2029.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
