OL,3,CMilitary gap years for school-leavers
OL,4,Cto be introduced before general
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe aim of the policy is to get young
OL,8,Fpeople interested in a future military
OL,9,Fcareer, while also giving them life
OL,10,Fskills and military training.
OL,12,F"What we've got to do is close the gap
OL,13,Fbetween those who volunteer to keep us
OL,14,Fsafe and the rest of society," he said.
OL,16,F"And I want to see a gap year scheme
OL,17,Fbrought in so that those who choose,
OL,18,Fafter leaving school or leaving
OL,19,Fcollege, can spend a year in the
OL,20,Fmilitary, get some great skills and
OL,21,Fexperience.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
