OL,7,F"And potentially other countries do
OL,8,Fthat. We can do that here as well."
OL,10,FAsked when the scheme would open up,
OL,11,Fhe said: "We're working on the details
OL,12,Fnow.
OL,14,F"I'm determined that in this
OL,15,FParliament we'll have that sort of
OL,16,Fscheme up and running. It helps the
OL,17,Fmilitary and it helps potentially
OL,18,Fthose who can gain life changing, life
OL,19,Fimproving experience from it."
