OL,7,FIt's not clear exactly how the scheme
OL,8,Fwould work, but the Australian model
OL,9,Fthe MoD has been recommended to follow
OL,10,Fwould be expensive to emulate.
OL,12,FIn Australia, school and college
OL,13,Fleavers are paid around the equivalent
OL,14,Fof #38,000 a year to train with the
OL,15,Farmy, navy or air force, but fully-
OL,16,Ftrained new soldiers in the UK get
OL,17,Fjust #23,500.
